# Background Music Folder

Place your background music files in this folder.

Supported formats: MP3, OGG, WAV

Recommended format: MP3 at 192-256kbps VBR for quality/size balance

For seamless looping, ensure your audio files:
- Have consistent volume at start and end points
- End at a natural loop point
- Are trimmed of silence at beginning/end

Example tracks:
- ambient-loop.mp3
- battle-theme.mp3
- mystery.mp3
- tavern.mp3
- dungeon.mp3
